Package: transformmatrix
Type: Package
Title: Convert 10x Sparse Matrices to Dense Format
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Nicole", "Schael", email = "nicole.schael@edu.unito.it",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools to read a 10x Genomics sparse matrix together with its
    barcodes and features, assign them to the columns and rows, convert the
    matrix to a dense representation and save it to disk. A front-end function
    is also provided to run the conversion inside a Docker container through a
    mounted volume.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    Matrix,
    data.table,
    utils
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
